{"tid":1796131,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"女同事成日講咸嘢點算？","createTime":"2019-12-24T11:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T07:28:40.000Z","uid":216662,"like":464,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"fb03ba189b9c08fe89532e4cb718d190ceaafec3","tid":1796131,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T11:44:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的。。。<br />\n<br />\n女同事24歲無男友又肥又矮又樣衰個口仲有啲臭,日日喺公司大大聲講咸嘢，開頭唔係同我講我都無理佢。<br />\n今日喺公司食晏佢坐埋嚟問我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />醜肥西：聖誕有咩搞？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我：陪女友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />醜肥西：佢話你就好啦今晚有嘢扑，我好耐無人搞，好想俾人屌到天光。。。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我：我飽啦，你慢慢食（其實我食咗一啖飯就起身）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />醜肥西細細聲：唉，無撚用！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我嬲得滯大聲係公司講：肥閪話平安夜想俾人屌通頂！有無人幫到佢！<br />\n最後有個靚仔男同事竟然攑手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個臭肥婆反而話靚仔無本心！<br />\n我心諗想點撚樣呀？真心想打撚死個肥婆 坐監算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無方法搞走佢？臭肥婆真係好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2344d50c0ebbbdff98f6b608e4460ce0c7b5868a","tid":1796131,"uid":56261,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T11:45:03.000Z","msg":"關你撚事"},{"pid":"4716df4b8baa988028207e2728ad7aad5be01729","tid":1796131,"uid":216662,"like":131,"dislike":4,"score":127,"quote":{"pid":"2344d50c0ebbbdff98f6b608e4460ce0c7b5868a","tid":1796131,"uid":56261,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T11:45:03.000Z","msg":"關你撚事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"臭肥西？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486f0faf36cb3402f69587caf44db84c212241e7","tid":1796131,"uid":144323,"like":212,"dislike":3,